Before we create our sass files, it's important to understand that there are twos syntaxes supported by sass
Scss Syntax
@mixin button-base(){
@include typography(button);

display: inline-flex;
position: relative;
height: $button-height;
border: none;
vertical-align:middle;

& hover{cursor:pointer;}

}

INDENTED SYNTAX
@mixin button-base()
@include typography(button)

display: inline-flex
position:relative
height:$button-height
border: none
vertical-align: middle

&: hover
cursosr: pointer
